General.Name: Blue World Acquisition Corporation Warrant
General.Description: Blue World Acquisition Corporation focuses on entering into a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, recapitalization, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. It intends to focus on businesses in the marine leisure, cruise, marine infrastructure and engineering, general hospitality, travel and tourism, and related industries. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in New York, New York.
